org.smpp.debug

Class DefaultDebug

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smpp.debug.DefaultDebug
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Debug

    public class DefaultDebug
extends Object
implements Debug
    Simple implementation of Debug interface which writes the trace lines to the System.out and provides simple indentation. This is the class whose instance is assigned as a default debug class to the SmppObject's debug object.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.1 $
    Author:
    Logica Mobile Networks SMPP Open Source Team
    See Also:
    Debug, SmppObject
